@startuml
title Filmoteca – Sequence Diagram (Browse and Add to Watchlist)

actor User
participant "Content\n(Content)" as Content
participant "Content\n(Details)" as Details
participant "User\n(Watchlist)" as Watchlist

User -> Content : Search for content
Content --> User : Return search results

User -> Details : Select content to view
Details --> User : Show content details

User -> Watchlist : Add content to watchlist
Watchlist --> User : Confirm addition
@enduml
